transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you so much for calling Viagra, my name is Jessie, can I get your first and—

Speaker 2: Last name?

Speaker 1: Yes, Jessie, my first name is Vincenzo, last name is Sclafani.

Speaker 2: Okay, great.

Speaker 1: Mr. Sclafani, can I get your zip code?

Speaker 2: 34990.

Speaker 1: Okay, thank you so much.

Speaker 2: I canceled my subscription, you know, a while ago, and I just saw you guys are charging—

Speaker 1: Me $162.

Speaker 2: I don't want it anymore, I canceled.

Speaker 1: Okay, bear with me just a moment, Mr. Sclafani.

Speaker 2: I appreciate it.

Speaker 1: Yeah, no problem, I'm so sorry.

Speaker 2: I see here that I don't see a, there's no call here, because otherwise if you call—

Speaker 1: We're more than happy to do it.

Speaker 2: And I don't see an email request, so no, we didn't receive anything saying that you wanted—

Speaker 1: To cancel.

Speaker 2: I called, it charged me, it's a lot of money, $162.

Speaker 1: Sure, no problem, I can go ahead and, let me go ahead and cancel that for you, and then—

Speaker 2: What I can do.

Speaker 1: I appreciate it.

Speaker 2: Yeah, no problem.

Speaker 1: What I could do is just keep your prescription active, so you can order when you want to.

Speaker 2: Okay?

Speaker 1: All right, okay.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Can I have my zip code, please?

Speaker 2: Can I have my money back?

Speaker 1: Like I just said, yeah, it's, I don't know if you heard me, but I said I processed the—

Speaker 2: Refund for you, okay?

Speaker 1: Oh, thank you so much.

Speaker 2: Yeah, no problem.

Speaker 1: And then we're just putting your account on demand, so that way your prescription remains—

Speaker 2: Active and you can order whenever you want to, okay?

Speaker 1: Thank you so much for your help.

Speaker 2: Jesse, your name is Jesse, right?

Speaker 1: Correct.

Speaker 2: Now bear in mind, everything is paused for you, you won't get any other refills and that—

Speaker 1: Kind of stuff.

Speaker 2: You remain active, and let's see here, any last things that we should be aware of?

Speaker 1: Yeah, so that's basically it.

Speaker 2: How long before I get my refund?

Speaker 1: How long before I get my refund?

Speaker 2: Why don't you just check your account now?

Speaker 1: You should already see it on there.

Speaker 2: Okay, all right.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: Thanks a lot.
